<hi rend="underline">Copy of letter received from the Connaught
<lb/>Rangers in Mesopotamia.</hi>

<opener><dateline><date>1.8.16</date></dateline></opener>

<lb/>The Secretary
<lb/>Irish Women's Association

<p>I enclose some lists of comforts which your Association has
<lb/>so kindly sent this regiment, and which have arrived and
<lb/>have been distributed.</p>

<p>I assure you that the comforts are very welcome, and
<lb/>that the men are very grateful to you for your generosity
<lb/>and kindness.</p>

<salute>(Signed)</salute> <signed>E.G. HAMILTON,</signed>
<lb/>Major
<lb/>O.C. The Connaught Rangers.
<lb/>I.E.F. "D".
        
    

    
                </body>
            </text>

        
            
        

         

    </group>
</text>
     

